  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="configuration">
    <title>Configuring Totem</title>

    <sect3><title>Configuration Information</title>

      <para>
        You may find that <application>totem</application> crashes. If so,
        you can set the following in your environment, either in ~/.xinitrc or in
        your .Xsession: <command>export CLUTTER_DISABLE_ARGB_VISUAL=1</command>
      </para>

    </sect3>

  </sect2>

